essential components : 
Server: A powerful computer that hosts our website. 
Web Server (Nginx): Software that manages user requests and serves web pages. 
Application Server: Software that processes code to create dynamic website content. 
Application Files (Codebase): Collection of code files that define website functionality.
 Database (MySQL): Software that stores website data.
 Domain Name (foobar.com): User-friendly name for the website. "www" DNS Record: Points to the server's IP address (A record).
